Class EncryptionConfig

java.lang.Object
com.myfinanceapp.security.EncryptionConfig
public final class EncryptionConfig extends Object
Configuration class for encryption-related constants and parameters. This class defines the configuration parameters for both AES and Argon2 encryption algorithms. It provides a centralized location for all encryption-related settings to ensure consistency and maintainability across the application.
